[2] TRUST ENGINE BAR
- Projects: 300+
- Regions: IR / IQ / OM / GCC
- Systems: 4 Core Systems

[3] SYSTEM DEFINITION BLOCK
- Left: What is AECS
- Right: Engineering Philosophy

[4] SYSTEM MODULE GRID
- Linear Ceiling System
- Grid Ceiling System
- Custom Engineering System
- Hybrid System

[5] ENGINEERING FLOW VISUAL
- Design → Engineering → Manufacturing → Execution

[6] PROJECT PROOF SECTION
- 3 featured case studies
- engineering breakdown preview

[7] EXECUTION SYSTEM PREVIEW
- site imagery + control overlay

[8] RFQ CTA ENGINE
- "Define your project as a system"

